38 including access to high-quality employment opportunities for residents of the State that
39 contribute to the development of a skilled and trained workforce;
40 14. Beneficial electrification. Coordinate with the commission and the Efficiency
41 Maine Trust, established in section 10103, to monitor beneficial electrification trends and
42 opportunities and to establish beneficial electrification targets and regulatory frameworks;
